'''不動產抵押貸款證券'''（Mortgage-backed security，MBS），[[資產抵押債券|資產抵押債券]]的一種，將以[[不動產|不動產]]為[[房地產抵押|抵押]]的貸款[[資產證券化|證券化]]後，以打包形式在市場上交易的[[金融工具|工具]]。

MBS在[[次按危機|次按危機]]中佔有很重要的角色<ref>{{cite news|title=With Rates Low, Banks Increase Mortgage Profit|url=https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2012/08/08/with-rate-twist-banks-increase-mortgage-profit/|accessdate=2020-07-11|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2012-08-08|author=Peter Eavis|format=Dealbook blog|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014542/https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2012/08/08/with-rate-twist-banks-increase-mortgage-profit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

